FBIS4-58848 "drnes089_j_94029" FBIS-NES-94-089 Daily Report 8 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen General Mobilization Under Way General Mobilization Under Way EA0905110094 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 2040 GMT 8 May 94 EA0905110094 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Excerpts] Military communique issued by the Defense Ministry: For the 12th day running, the total destructive war declared by General 'Ali Abdallah Salih, the Sanaa military gang leader, against our people and heroic Armed Forces, has continued. [passage omitted] Today witnessed [words indistinct] mobilization with thousands of our people's sons, people from public and private institutions, responding to the decree of Defense Minister Haytham Qasim Tahir, who has ordered a general mobilization for the protection of life and property. Thousands of citizens went to the camps in response to the call to do their national duty of protecting our people, their property, and land [words indistinct] being waged by the oppressive al-Ahmar gang. [passage omitted]
